{"tid":1528652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下各位手足聽日唔好塞路同破壞啲入閘機啊！！！","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T15:06:14.000Z","uid":315909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2d87f33387c68114f285fc52cd55c1ec1fea5ff9","tid":1528652,"uid":315909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"你地整爛啲入閘機咁後面啲人點樣俾錢搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其喺油塘啊、金鐘啊、九龍塘啊<br />\n你地跳閘好喇 跳閘後面啲人都有得俾錢 黨鐵都仲叫有錢收<br />\n仲有呀 有車嘅手足千祈唔好將架車打橫泊喺啲隧道口啊 <br />\n紅隧 東隧 仲有啲公路一塞就仆街喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地咁樣做搞到大塞車唔想罷工啲人點樣翻工？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2fTdiv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2fTdiv.jpg&h=12d3cb94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下大家千祈唔好啊！！！"},{"pid":"e7357c7bd9d2c9ff65ce0085f45a2569295abba0","tid":1528652,"uid":224149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c181cf755762ed2926ae1a16ea0fa75aae0e06ad","tid":1528652,"uid":224149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6649fc568dfa0d2858c522d310d24bd717d943d","tid":1528652,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧鳴而死 不默而生<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e42dc8ecb42396a8da35fda9a7d88add68279596","tid":1528652,"uid":224149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"061f59bae315b3fdca53ccc6f8590b3d4f086ac9","tid":1528652,"uid":224149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:44:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e516efbab7716783c626a765dba517a8a25752b","tid":1528652,"uid":224149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":